compodoc
	npm i --save @compodoc/compodoc

compodoc -p src/tsconfig.json -s -w
	As you understand,Compodoc is a documentation tool for Angualr applications
what are the key features compodoc
	-full Angular API support
	-display each API by type:module,component,directive,service,class,pipe
	-and also application routing
	-application documentaion coverage support
	-other Typescript files like interfaces or simple enums,types or varibles
	-Additional documentation

Advantages
	-offline tool using Node.js
	-no source code upload online for metadata scanning
	-no local Type
